{"title": "How to create a ward/room in Admission?", "body": "Follow these steps to generate a ward or room:\n  1. Go to Settings.\n  2. Navigate to Licensing & Features.\n  3. Select Admission.\n  4. Click the Room & Bed Icon for the designated Facility.\n  5. Choose Create New and select Ward or Room.\n  When creating a ward, provide essential information such as Ward Name, Specialty, Ward Type, and Description. Then click Save or Save & Add New if adding another ward if necessary.\n  When creating a room, input the Room Name and Description before clicking Save. Alternatively, click Save & Add New to add another Room if needed.\n      If you need further assistance please contact support on 1300 103 903 or email at support@medirecords.com"}